description: Please welcome Selina to Wiredpussy. Selina arrives for the shoot with a bit of a cocky attitude. She thinks she can handle anything, but Princess Donna quickly challenges this little tattooed slut to see if she is really as tough as she thinks. After getting cattleprodded, clamped, and electrified in every way possible Selina learns a thing or two about humility and respect.
title: Selina
